# game/intro.rpy:6
translate simplified_chinese start_b7652f4f:

    # p "{i}Sigh…{/i}"
    p "（哈…）"

# game/intro.rpy:8
translate simplified_chinese start_174bcc93:

    # p "{i}What a hot day today is… I’m all sweaty…I’ll have to take a bath again…{/i}"
    p "（今天好热啊…出了好多的汗…又要洗澡了…）"

# game/intro.rpy:10
translate simplified_chinese start_406a25a4:

    # "It was Saturday afternoon. After a series of unfortunate events, I am now just lazing around in my room."
    "那是一个星期六的下午。在经历了各种不幸的事件之后，人鱼正在家中无所事事。"

# game/intro.rpy:12
translate simplified_chinese start_a42e3439:

    # p "{i}I mean, I was a bit hungry so I went to the convenience store to get some food, but the moment I stepped outside my house it started raining! The weather said it’s sunny today! Not to mention that speeding car that splashed mud all over me…{/i}"
    p "（可是，因为肚子有点饿了就想着去趟便利店，结果好不容易出门一趟还突然下起了雨！）"
    p "（明明天气预报中播报员很有精神地说了「今天是晴天」的！就这么开始下了，而且还不注意被一辆快车溅起的泥弄脏了衣服）"

# game/intro.rpy:14
translate simplified_chinese start_c4072197:

    # p "{i}…geez!{/i}"
    p "（…真是的！）"

# game/intro.rpy:16
translate simplified_chinese start_5da35a2d:

    # p "{i}And right when I thought that it couldn’t get any worse, I realized I was lost because of the huge downpour!{/i}"
    p "（更为糟糕的是、刚想着「今天不会再倒霉下去了吧？」就意识到了自己因为雨太大而迷路了）"

# game/intro.rpy:18
translate simplified_chinese start_42e5e618:

    # p "{i}After all that, I didn’t even get to buy my favourite chips and lunch! Ugh!{/i}"
    p "（结果到头来人鱼都没买到最喜欢的薯条，甚至连其他午饭都没买到，唉！）"

# game/intro.rpy:20
translate simplified_chinese start_8ec461dd:

    # p "{i}…wait. It’s during these times that SSRs are pulled from gacha, right?{/i}"
    p "（等下...这种时候是不是就能抽到SSR了？）"

# game/intro.rpy:22
translate simplified_chinese start_358b03b8:

    # p "{i}Let’s pull!!!!{/i}"
    p "（赶快去试试吧！！！）"

# game/intro.rpy:24
translate simplified_chinese start_690ba078:

    # "But in the end, not even a single SR card came out."
    "结果到最后，甚至是SR都没被抽到。"

# game/intro.rpy:26
translate simplified_chinese start_769eb3d2:

    # p "{i}Sigh…yeah right, what was I expecting…{/i}"
    p "（唉，这也正常，人鱼在想什么...）"

# game/intro.rpy:28
translate simplified_chinese start_6525d3f6:

    # p "{i}I want this terrible day to hurry up and end already…{/i}"
    p "（真希望这样的糟糕日子早点结束啊…）"

# game/intro.rpy:30
translate simplified_chinese start_df717f66:

    # "As soon as that thought came to mind…"
    "刚这么想着时..."

# game/intro.rpy:35
translate simplified_chinese start_03622086:

    # "…the doorbell rang."
    "...门铃响了。"

# game/intro.rpy:37
translate simplified_chinese start_acb1fbda:

    # "???" "Hello! Delivery!"
    "？？？" "「你好！你的快递！」"

# game/intro.rpy:39
translate simplified_chinese start_f8869760:

    # p "{i}A delivery? I wonder what it is.{/i}"
    p "（快递？会是什么呢？）"

# game/intro.rpy:41
translate simplified_chinese start_fe4e8d19:

    # "Mailman" "Here is your delivery. For ummm, Hitona Kohigashi, correct? Please sign here."
    "快递员" "「这个就是你的快递。那个...「小东人鱼」是吗？请在这里签字」"

# game/intro.rpy:43
translate simplified_chinese start_055bce01:

    # p "Ah yes, okay…"
    p "「嗯是的，好的...」"

# game/intro.rpy:45
translate simplified_chinese start_b27c6b62:

    # "Just like that, a huge box was left at the front door."
    "就这样，一个大箱子被放到了地上。"

# game/intro.rpy:47
translate simplified_chinese start_d5535be6:

    # "On top of the box was a letter. I picked it up and read it."
    "箱子上面有一封信，人鱼拿起读了起来。"

# game/intro.rpy:51
translate simplified_chinese start_87f754cd:

    # nvl_narrator "“Kohi!"
    nvl_narrator "『致小东！"

# game/intro.rpy:53
translate simplified_chinese start_e4a65c3e:

    # nvl_narrator "You left this in your old room! Can’t believe you forgot to bring something so big! Be thankful that you have such a reliable senpai! Hope we can meet sometime!"
    nvl_narrator "　小东！这是你旧房子落下的东西哦！你能把这么大的东西忘了也算你厉害！好好感谢你这个可靠的前辈吧！期待什么时候再和你见面！"

# game/intro.rpy:55
translate simplified_chinese start_3d5b3c63:

    # nvl_narrator "Senpai”"
    nvl_narrator "最爱你的前辈』"

# game/intro.rpy:57
translate simplified_chinese start_b50b7f74:

    # nvl clear
    # p "{i}So it was from senpai…it’s been quite a while since I last met her.{/i}"
    nvl clear
    p "（果然是前辈寄来的啊…和前辈好久没见了呢）"

# game/intro.rpy:61
translate simplified_chinese start_2dd86e32:

    # p "{i}But really, what is she talking about? I don’t think I would forget to bring something so huge…right?{/i}"
    p "（但是，她说这是人鱼忘在旧屋子的东西？但是就像她说的一样，人鱼怎么可能把这么大的东西忘了呢！）"

# game/intro.rpy:63
translate simplified_chinese start_5ab92f24:

    # p "{i}Well, let’s see what’s inside first.{/i}"
    p "（好吧，先看看里面是什么）"

# game/intro.rpy:65
translate simplified_chinese start_358032da:

    # p "{i}It’s a…safe?{/i}"
    p "（这是...保险箱？）"

# game/intro.rpy:67
translate simplified_chinese start_f8fa44a9:

    # "It was a silver-coloured safe with a 4-digit lock affixed to it."
    "包装里是一个银色的保险箱，但是被4位密码锁锁着。"

# game/intro.rpy:69
translate simplified_chinese start_2f060ecc:

    # p "{i}Hmmm, I don’t think I ever had a safe like this.{/i}"
    p "（嗯...人鱼不记得自己有保险箱啊）"

# game/intro.rpy:71
translate simplified_chinese start_cd3bbe5e:

    # p "{i}Let’s just bring this inside and ask senpai what it’s all about.{/i}"
    p "（总之先带回家，再问问前辈这是什么吧）"

# game/intro.rpy:73
translate simplified_chinese start_435b4fc4:

    # "Thinking that, I put the rather heavy safe inside and texted senpai asking about it."
    "人鱼一边想着，一边把意外很沉的保险箱搬到了家里，发消息问了前辈。"

# game/intro.rpy:75
translate simplified_chinese start_02a33c06:

    # "After sending the text, I went back to lazing in my chair and staring blankly at the monitor."
    "然后消息发出去之后就一直坐在电竞椅上盯着显示器发呆。"

# game/intro.rpy:77
translate simplified_chinese start_f10cac22:

    # p "{i}What to do…{/i}"
    p "（该干啥呢...）"

# game/intro.rpy:81
translate simplified_chinese start_e960d988:

    # "As soon I got lost in thought, a message came."
    "就在人鱼陷入思考的时候，有一个消息来了。"

# game/intro.rpy:83
translate simplified_chinese start_68e03f06:

    # "“Kohigashiii! I found an interesting questionnaire! Hurry up and try it!”"
    "『小东————！我发现了一个很有趣的问卷测试！快去试试！』"

# game/intro.rpy:85
translate simplified_chinese start_b26c9a7a:

    # p "{i}Oh?{/i}"
    p "（哦？）"

# game/intro.rpy:87
translate simplified_chinese start_7d3ed7f5:

    # p "{i}That’s kinda rare and…random.{/i}"
    p "（这种的比较稀有，而且是随机的）"

# game/intro.rpy:89
translate simplified_chinese start_a22b8ab7:

    # p "{i}Oh well, let’s try it.{/i}"
    p "（好吧，人鱼试试）"

# game/intro.rpy:91
translate simplified_chinese start_84892ae3:

    # "I opened the questionnaire linked."
    "人鱼点击了问卷的链接。"

# game/intro.rpy:126
translate simplified_chinese start_37195d21:

    # "The questions came one by one, never seeming to end."
    "有很多问题一个接一个地出现了，看起来根本看不完。"

# game/intro.rpy:128
translate simplified_chinese start_8fec4b0a:

    # "10. Your favorite day of the year?"
    "10. 你最喜欢的节日？"

# game/intro.rpy:130
translate simplified_chinese start_636fde49:

    # p "{i}There’s so many of them though…{/i}"
    p "（好像有很多...）"

# game/intro.rpy:132
translate simplified_chinese start_e03763da:

    # "45. When do you think you’ll meet your soulmate?"
    "45. 当你和你的梦中情人相遇的时候你会想什么？"

# game/intro.rpy:134
translate simplified_chinese start_9be23a2f:

    # p "{i}It’s asking me about the future now??{/i}"
    p "（诶？是说未来的呢还是现在的呢？）"

# game/intro.rpy:136
translate simplified_chinese start_9879a7dd:

    # "70. What is your favourite movie genre?"
    "70. 你喜欢哪种类型的电影？"

# game/intro.rpy:138
translate simplified_chinese start_61f40da3:

    # p "{i}It asks this 70 questions in?!{/i}"
    p "（70个问题就为了问这些？！）"

# game/intro.rpy:140
translate simplified_chinese start_90a8dd45:

    # "155. How much time do you spend each day sitting down?"
    "155. 你每天在电脑前坐多久？"

# game/intro.rpy:142
translate simplified_chinese start_9b2ece79:

    # p "{i}Really? What does this have to do with anything?? And 155 questions in??!{/i}"
    p "（不是吧…这和之前的问题有关系吗？？说起来，这已经是第155个问题了？？！）"

# game/intro.rpy:144
translate simplified_chinese start_f995123e:

    # p "{i}Why am I even still doing this…{/i}"
    p "（真是的，人鱼为什么要一直做这个啊...）"

# game/intro.rpy:146
translate simplified_chinese start_b9e7965e:

    # "Final question."
    "最后一个问题。"

# game/intro.rpy:148
translate simplified_chinese start_137d67c2:

    # p "{i}Finally…{/i}"
    p "（终于要结束了...）"

# game/intro.rpy:164
translate simplified_chinese start_b041809e:

    # p "{i}Finally done! What’s the result of this questionnaire?{/i}"
    p "（终于完了！结果会是什么呢？）"

# game/intro.rpy:168
translate simplified_chinese start_2e788052:

    # "“You are compassionate towards yourself. A good trait to have! It’s important to care for yourself.”"
    "『你对自己很体贴。有这个性格是好事！珍惜自己很重要。』"

# game/intro.rpy:170
translate simplified_chinese start_1e443c2a:

    # "“You are compassionate towards everyone else. Your friends must be lucky to have you around.”"
    "『你对别人也很体贴。你的朋友会很幸运居然有你这么温柔的人！』"

# game/intro.rpy:172
translate simplified_chinese start_75b29d5d:

    # "“You are compassionate towards both yourself and others. It’s good to love everyone, yourself included.”"
    "『你对自己和别人都很体贴。去爱每一个人包括你自己是很好的一件事！』"

# game/intro.rpy:175
translate simplified_chinese start_c7406311:

    # "“You think you are cute. Hey, no one is judging, and you really are cute!”"
    "『你认为你很可爱。放心，没人会阻止你这么说，毕竟事实就是如此』"

# game/intro.rpy:177
translate simplified_chinese start_77b15b75:

    # "“You think everyone else is cute. A lot of people are cute on the outside, but you are able to see beyond that, and appreciate the cuteness within their hearts as well.”"
    "『虽然你认为其他人也都很可爱、但是你不止能看到外表的可爱，你也能看到别人内心的可爱』"

# game/intro.rpy:179
translate simplified_chinese start_da57af4a:

    # "“You think everyone is cute. When everything in the world is cute, the world becomes a better place!”"
    "『你觉得每个人都很可爱。如果这个世界上的一切都很可爱的话，世界一定会变得更好！』"

# game/intro.rpy:182
translate simplified_chinese start_354325e9:

    # "“You are a cheerful person. Always looking forward to what you’re going to do next!”"
    "『你是个很有活力的人。总是会期待着你接下来要做的事情』"

# game/intro.rpy:184
translate simplified_chinese start_6832af1f:

    # "“You are especially cheerful when around others. Like a bright ray of sunshine, you’re a blessing that everyone is grateful for.”"
    "『当你和别人在一起时，你会特别高兴。就像一缕明亮的阳光，你是每个人都感激的祝福。』"

# game/intro.rpy:186
translate simplified_chinese start_6d8a74d3:

    # "“You are an infinite source of cheerfulness. Everyone around you immediately becomes cheerful just being near you. I have no idea how, but I want one of you right here in my home!”"
    "『你是无头无尽的快乐源泉。你周围的每个人只要靠近你就会立刻变得快乐起来。虽然不知道怎么做，但我想把你带回家。』"

# game/intro.rpy:189
translate simplified_chinese start_85507afc:

    # "“You think deeply about yourself. You often get lost in thought about matters pertaining to yourself.”"
    "『你会仔细考虑自己的事情。如果和自己有关系的话，你会很容易陷入沉思。』"

# game/intro.rpy:191
translate simplified_chinese start_5af03d12:

    # "“You think deeply about the situations of others. You are prone to getting lost in thought when thinking about others but quick and decisive about your own affairs.”"
    "『你会仔细考虑别人的事情。容易陷入别人的思考中，如果和自己有关系的话就可以迅速做出决断。』"

# game/intro.rpy:193
translate simplified_chinese start_67c4dce5:

    # "“You are a deep thinker. You enjoy thinking thoroughly about anything and everything. Be careful going too deep.”"
    "『你是喜欢深思熟虑的人。你喜欢什么都好好思考一下。但是要注意不要想得太多！』"

# game/intro.rpy:196
translate simplified_chinese start_b9848d5e:

    # "“You are an innocent person. No one in this world is more innocent than you. White as snow, just like a baby.”"
    "『你是个天真无邪的人，比谁都天真。像雪一样白，就像婴儿一样。』"

# game/intro.rpy:198
translate simplified_chinese start_f2c34ee7:

    # "“You believe that no one is truly guilty of anything. All actions are predetermined, thus no one can be guilty.”"
    "『你相信没有人真的有罪。所有的行为都是预先确定的，因此没有人会有罪。』"

# game/intro.rpy:218
translate simplified_chinese start_860aaef6:

    # "“You believe that everyone in this world is innocent. Of course, including yourself."
    "『你相信这个世界上的每个人都是无辜的。当然，包括你自己。』"

# game/intro.rpy:219
translate simplified_chinese start_938818d9:

    # "As long as everyone is able to forgive each other and not repeat their mistakes, the world will be as pure as the driven snow.”"
    "『只要每个人都能互相原谅，不再犯之前的错误，世界就会像雪一样纯洁。』"

# game/intro.rpy:203
translate simplified_chinese start_e4c8dde6:

    # "“You are very ambitious about your goals. Nothing in this world can stop you once you start working.”"
    "『你对自己的目标很有热情。一旦你开始做某件事，谁也阻止不了你！』"

# game/intro.rpy:205
translate simplified_chinese start_0e96fbb6:

    # "“You are very ambitious when supporting others. You stop at nothing to help those around you reach their goals.”"
    "『你是很有热心帮助别人的人！一旦开始帮助别人，因为任何事情都不会阻止你去帮助别人直到达成目标』"

# game/intro.rpy:207
translate simplified_chinese start_b49418a7:

    # "“You are a very ambitious person. No matter what it is, you always want to give it 100%%, no, 200%% effort!”"
    "『你是一个很有野心的人，不管对于什么事情，你都想用100%，不，甚至200%的精力完成』"

# game/intro.rpy:210
translate simplified_chinese start_62554d0a:

    # "“You are a very calm person. When it involves you, you are able to think calmly without panicking, and quickly reach a solution without struggle.”"
    "『你是一个非常冷静的人。当一件事情涉及到你时，你能够冷静地思考而不惊慌失措，并且不费吹灰之力就能迅速找到解决方案。』"

# game/intro.rpy:231
translate simplified_chinese start_f58189b3:

    # "“You are very calm when it comes to the predicaments of others. You are able to solve their problems without breaking a sweat."
    "『当遇到别人的困境时，你非常冷静。你可以毫不费力地解决他们的问题。』"

# game/intro.rpy:232
translate simplified_chinese start_289524e1:

    # "But the opposite is true when it comes to yourself. Perhaps it’s because you are putting yourself out of the equation?”"
    "『但对你自己来说，情况恰恰相反。也许这是因为你把自身至于度外』"

# game/intro.rpy:214
translate simplified_chinese start_690f00c2:

    # "“You are a very calm person. The most calm person in the world. Nothing in the world can perturb you.”"
    "『你是非常冷静的人。是世界上最冷静的人。这个世界上没有什么能让你着急的。』"

# game/intro.rpy:216
translate simplified_chinese start_bb0ddf5c:

    # p "{i}…That’s it??? After all those questions, that’s it???? Give me back my time!{/i}"
    p "（…欸？这么多问题的结果就这些？把人鱼的时间还回来啊！）"

# game/intro.rpy:218
translate simplified_chinese start_7766d36a:

    # "I looked outside and the clock, and it was already midnight."
    "一看表，已经是深夜了。"

# game/intro.rpy:220
translate simplified_chinese start_22bd1d81:

    # p "{i}How did that questionnaire took so much time…uugh…I feel sleepy…{/i}"
    p "（啊（哈欠）...回答那个问卷测试的时候时间过的好快，呜，已经开始困了）"

# game/intro.rpy:222
translate simplified_chinese start_0731b79e:

    # p "{i}I’ll just go sleep…{/i}"
    p "（要不睡吧...）"

# game/intro.rpy:228
translate simplified_chinese start_0ff44e2c:

    # p "{i}Uuugh…is it a call…ughh{/i}"
    p "（嗯...是电话吗？）"

# game/intro.rpy:230
translate simplified_chinese start_cb0045c3:

    # "I picked up the phone; it was senpai calling."
    "手机上显示着前辈的来电。"

# game/intro.rpy:235
translate simplified_chinese start_8c8d6e6b:

    # p "…Hello…Morning…"
    p "「喂...？早上好...」"

# game/intro.rpy:237
translate simplified_chinese start_29f02520:

    # sn "Kohiiii! Morniiing! Can you meet me at the park right now?"
    sn "「小东————！早上好！你能现在来公园和我见一面吗？」"

# game/intro.rpy:239
translate simplified_chinese start_04a59adf:

    # sn "There’s something I want to give you. Well, just hurry up and come! I’ll be waiting!"
    sn "「我有东西要给你。别犹豫了，快点来啊，我等你」"

# game/intro.rpy:244
translate simplified_chinese start_0c67745b:

    # p "{i}She hung up…I didn’t even get to say a single word…{/i}"
    p "（人鱼还没说什么电话就挂断了...）"

# game/intro.rpy:246
translate simplified_chinese start_b868d1e4:

    # "Senpai seemed very excited, but she didn’t reply to my message yesterday."
    "前辈看起来很高兴，但是她昨天并没有回复人鱼信息。"

# game/intro.rpy:248
translate simplified_chinese start_60193cfd:

    # p "{i}Well, might as well meet her and ask her directly.{/i}"
    p "（也好，去一趟当面问她吧）"

# game/intro.rpy:250
translate simplified_chinese start_86e99581:

    # "I got ready to go out and meet senpai."
    "人鱼准备好了就去见前辈了。"

# game/intro.rpy:252
translate simplified_chinese start_fb2e0ffc:

    # "Before leaving, I looked around the place a bit, and caught sight of the safe."
    "在出发前，人鱼四处环顾了一下，并且看到了那个保险箱。"

# game/intro.rpy:254
translate simplified_chinese start_b7652f4f_1:

    # p "{i}Sigh…{/i}"
    p "（唉...）"

# game/intro.rpy:256
translate simplified_chinese start_9dc7057a:

    # p "{i}Let’s go then!{/i}"
    p "（那么，人鱼出发了！）"

